name: Button::Style
detail:
This type is a string.

On macOS it can have following possible values:
* `"rounded"`
* `"regular-square"`
* `"thick-square"`
* `"thicker-square"`
* `"disclosure"`
* `"shadowless-square"`
* `"circular"`
* `"textured-square"`
* `"help-button"`
* `"small-square"`
* `"textured-rounded"`
* `"round-rect"`
* `"recessed"`
* `"rounded-disclosure"`
* `"inline"`
